title: Country Living and Ocean Close Ocean & River Peek 99353
text:
Country Living and Ocean Close Ocean & River Peek 99353 ad date: 10/21/2015 
99353 Winchuck River Rd., Brookings Unique property with so many extras. 3 BD/2 BA bright home with hardwood floors. Sunny kitchen and dining room with views of the charming gardens and flowers. Two car garage with ocean view bonus room/guest quarters that has its own bathroom. Large deck and river view orchard with fruit trees, too. No. 15318323 $239,900 Sarah Pettinger
